title: Ep 20 | Jase's Earwigs, Phil's Ants, and Al’s Plagues
description:
In one of the wildest stories ever, Jase gets attacked by an earwig (no, it's not folklore!), Phil and Blue get caught in a fire ant bed, and Al covers his ears while talking about Moses and the plagues.

See episodes of "Unashamed with Phil Robertson": https://bit.ly/2J4XsiX

See clips from Phil's TV show "In the Woods with Phil": https://bit.ly/2PNM6k1
